# Design Tokens

Full spec: `.ai/design-system/colors-spacing.md`

## Use tokens from `styles/tokens.css`

- Colors: `--light-bg`, `--dark-bg`, `--accent-brand`, `--muted-text`, etc.
- Spacing: `--space-*`, `--space-section`
- Type scale: `--text-xs` through `--text-display`
- Layout: `--container-max`, `--container-padding`

## Do not

- Add new hex colors inline in components
- Hardcode `120px` section padding - use `--space-section`
- Redefine `--font-*` outside `app/globals.css`

## Whitespace

Enterprise B2B = generous section padding, clear visual hierarchy, minimal palette.
